rows.text_2:
@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Come on, @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name, it's time to get ready for bed.

@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: But I still have so much homework to do!

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: Hmm, this is the third night in a row that you haven’t gone to bed on time because of homework.

@data.characters.f3_mother.name: "How can we make sure you get all your work done and still get to bed on time so that you get enough sleep?”

@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Maybe I can start earlier?”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Shall we make a rule that you start your homework half an hour after you get home from school? That way, you can finish it and have some time to eat and relax before bed, too! I am happy to help you remember when to start.”

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Okay, @data.characters.f3_mother.name.”

*The next day.*

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “@data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name, have you started your homework yet?”

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “I'll start now, @data.characters.f3_mother.name! But can you help me with this one problem? I was having trouble with it yesterday.”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Of course, my dear.”

*Later that same day.*

 @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name: “Look, @data.characters.f3_mother.name, I'm ready for bed earlier tonight!”

 @data.characters.f3_mother.name: “Well done, @data.characters.f3_daughter_7.name. I’m proud that we figured that problem out together. Now you can be well-rested for tomorrow, and your homework is complete!”
